snippet.title: Dushmanto Raja Jadi Hotam Ami | Anutap | Bengali Movie Video Song | Kumar Sanu Song

localized.description:
Anutap was released on  1992 Bengali film Raj Babbar Debashree Roy  Anup Kumar Robi Ghosh Dipankar Dey Nirmal Kumar Soumitra Banerjee Master Shivam  Sanghamitra Banerjee Angel The Bengali film is  Directed  by  Prabhat Roy scored the music in the film. 

Watch bengali movie song "Dushmanto Raja Jadi Hotam Ami ; দুস্মন্ত রাজা যদি হতাম আমি' sang by Kumar Sanu.

Song Name : Dushmanto Raja Jadi Hotam Ami
Artist :Kumar Sanu
Lyricist :Pulak Bandopadhyay
Music Director :Bappi Lahiri
Movie :Anutap
Release :1992
Director :Prabhat Roy
Star Cast :Raj Babbar, Debasree Roy
